reviewText: I liked it a lot. Great story line lots of action and the acting superb.  I would recomend it to my friends.
Richard Gonzales and Rockwood are at their best in this continuation of the Bullitt Series. An amazing effort and extremely entertaining. A must see piece of Big Island film history!
If you love the work from the Golden Age of Roger Corman (Deathrace, Grand Theft Auto ,Night of the Cobra Woman) you will full enjoy Bullitt!
